Jennifer Lee said herself that "Elsa was born on the Winter Solstice", which does NOT fall on the 21st or 22nd every year. Disney's official Tumblr page celebrated her birthday on the Winter Solstice of 2015, which was December 22nd that year. Jennifer Lee never says that Elsa's birthday is on the 21st or 22nd. It is simply celebrated on the Winter Solstice, whose date can change every year. Until we get a concrete date confirmed by the creators themselves, the birth date is the Winter Solstice.
